snippet.title: FROGGONIT - Demo Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
FROGGONIT was trying to be the best explorer but accidentally covered the island with darkness!
Hop into this comedy adventure game full of secrets and help your animal friends restore the light!

Demo available for the Steam Next Fest, 9 Oct 2023:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2276040/FROGGONIT/
